<dl id="n06067k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06067k">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06067k"> 67(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> milk / not sojourn in / metal</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>Le lait</mark>, apr&egrave;s &eacute;bullition, ainsi que l&apos;eau, seront vers&eacute;s dans des <i>r&egrave;cipients en porcelaine</i>, afin de <mark>ne pas s&eacute;journer dans des vases en m&eacute;tal</mark>. <font color="green">[The milk, after boiling, as well as the water, will be poured into porcelain containers, so as not to remain in metal containers.]</font> <small> ?. ?, <a name="LARA" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#LARA"><cite title="source">La Revue Philantropique</cite></a> (????) 229</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
